From v5.5.1 HEKTAR

<event name="START_HEKTAR">
	<metaVariable name="juke_hektar" op="set" val="1"/>
	<preventQuest/>
	<beaconType id="map_icon_start" global="false">
		<color r="46" g="252" b="51" a="1"/>
	</beaconType>
	<text>Even after closing your Atlas, the torrent of advertisements doesn't stop. Just about every product imaginable is shilled to you in under a minute. You finally resort to muting the ship's radio so you can hear yourself think again.</text>
	<variable name="loc_unique_sectors" op="add" val="1"/>
	<img back="BACK_EVENT_HEKTAR" planet="NONE"/>
	<ship load="SHIP_GUARD_HEKTAR" hostile="false"/>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event load="GUARD_HEKTAR"/>
	</choice>
</event>

<event name="GUARD_HEKTAR">
	<text>"Greetingsssss, valued cussstomersss! Welcome to Hektar Indusssstriesss (tm)'sss Hektar MEGA-MARKET(tm). It'sss alwaysss wonderful to ssssee new debtorsss in thessse partsss!"</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Thanks - wait, did you just call us debtors?</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Oh ho, another one! You new arrivalssss alwayssss ssseem ssso sssurprissed. Yessss, I'm afraid you are in masssssive debt to Hektar Indussstriesss! Didn't you know that every U.W.U. point you collect comessss with a fee of 625 ssscrap? Yesssir, you now owe ussss a total of 2500 ssscrap! Quite the predicament..."</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Well, what do we do about it?</text>
				<event>
					<text>"Oh that'sss quite sssimple. You pay it, or you ssstay here forever. Don't worry if you do end up ssstaying, Hektar Indussstriessss sssellsss just about everything you need to live a painfully adequate life of a minimum wage worker! Good luck!"</text>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Surely there's SOMETHING we can do!</text>
						<event>
							<text>The Slug laughs. "Yeah, ssssure. You could go track down Mr. Billy Hektar himssself and asssk for your debt to be cleared! Hah, get real."</text>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>Blast these assholes.</text>
								<event>
									<text>This is criminal! If the Federation isn't aware about this, then you'll have to take matters into your own hands, starting with this ship.</text>
									<ship hostile="true"/>
									<choice hidden="true">
										<text>Continue...</text>
										<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
									</choice>
								</event>
							</choice>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>Leave.</text>
								<event>
									<text>The guard waves you goodbye as you distance yourself.</text>
									<choice hidden="true">
										<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
										<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
									</choice>
									<choice hidden="true">
										<text>Do nothing.</text>
										<event/>
									</choice>
								</event>
							</choice>
						</event>
					</choice>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>We'll have to figure this out later. Leave.</text>
						<event>
							<text>The guard waves you goodbye as you distance yourself.</text>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
								<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
							</choice>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>Do nothing.</text>
								<event/>
							</choice>
						</event>
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>

<ship name="SHIP_GUARD_HEKTAR" auto_blueprint="MU_HEKTAR_GUARD">
	<surrender min="999" max="999" load="GUARD_SIGNAL"/>
	<destroyed load="GUARD_HEKTAR_DESTROY"/>
	<deadCrew load="GUARD_HEKTAR_DEADCREW"/>
	<crew>
		<crewMember type="slug_hektar" prop="0.75"/>
		<crewMember type="lizard" prop="0.25"/>
	</crew>
</ship>

<event name="GUARD_HEKTAR_DESTROY">
	<text>You have defeated the Hektar guard. Whatever might have been in their cargo has for certain been destroyed, but you can at least salvage some supplies from the ship.</text>
	<autoReward level="MED">standard</autoReward>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event load="GUARD_HEKTAR_FOLLOWUP"/>
	</choice>
</event>







