<textList name="TEXT_GUARD_SIGNAL">
	<text>It appears the guard ship is sending out a distress signal to a nearby ASB platform! Brace for impact!</text>
	<text>Scans show the guard has sent a request for backup from an ASB defense system. That can't be good...</text>
	<text>You catch chatter on the other ship, mentioning something about a signal requesting for ASB backup! Looks like we might have another hazard to worry about.</text>
</textList>
<event name="GUARD_SIGNAL">
	<text load="TEXT_GUARD_SIGNAL"/>
	<choice hidden="true" req="PDS_DISABLE">
		<text>(Signal Diluter) Jam their signal.</text>
		<event>
			<text>When no ASB activates, you assume that is a good sign that your augment has functioned properly, and you continue to fight.</text>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event>
			<environment type="PDS" target="player"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>

<eventList name="GUARD_MIND">
	<event>
		<text>The captain struggles to keep the ship on track, but the rest of the crew seems to know something is up and keeps the ship on target.</text>
		<status type="limit" target="enemy" system="pilot" amount="0"/>
		<ship hostile="true"/>
		<choice hidden="true">
			<text>Continue...</text>
			<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
		</choice>
	</event>
	<event>
		<text>Your mind control proves effective and the guard ship goes silent.</text>
		<ship hostile="false"/>
	</event>
</eventList>

<eventList name="GUARD_CLOAK">
	<event>
		<text>You try to cloak and evade the enemy ship, but their scanners are too good and they lock onto your location!</text>
		<ship hostile="true"/>
		<choice hidden="true">
			<text>Continue...</text>
			<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
		</choice>
	</event>
	<event>
		<text>You try to cloak and evade the enemy ship, but their scanners are too good and they lock onto your location!</text>
		<ship hostile="true"/>
		<choice hidden="true">
			<text>Continue...</text>
			<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
		</choice>
	</event>
	<event>
		<text>You successfully manage to slip past the guard without being noticed.</text>
		<ship hostile="false"/>
	</event>
</eventList>

<eventList name="GUARD_ESCAPE">
	<event>
		<text>You attempt to slip past the guard, but they're faster than expected and catch up to you!</text>
		<ship hostile="true"/>
		<choice hidden="true">
			<text>Continue...</text>
			<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
		</choice>
	</event>
	<event>
		<text>You successfully manage to escape from the guard's range.</text>
		<ship hostile="false"/>
	</event>
</eventList>


