					FEDERATION
\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\
\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\
\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\
\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\


<textList name="TEXT_START_FED">
	<text>You have arrived in Federation space. The Federation may be weakened, but this sector remains fully functional. The Rebellion will struggle to sneak its way into here.</text>
	<text>You have arrived in Federation space. Lots of friendly faces will be here, but there will be plenty of Rebel scum invading as well.</text>
	<text>You have arrived in Federation space. This may be a sector full of allies, but it is bound to attract plenty of Rebels too.</text>
</textList>
<event name="START_FED">
	<preventQuest/>
	<beaconType id="map_icon_start" global="false">
		<color r="46" g="252" b="51" a="1"/>
	</beaconType>
	<text load="TEXT_START_FED"/>
	<ship load="SHIP_GUARD_FED" hostile="false"/>
	<customFleet right="true" firing="true" autoDarkening="false">CUSTOM_FLEET_FED</customFleet>
	<changeBackground>BACK_SECTOR_FEDERATION</changeBackground>
	<playSound>lightspeed</playSound>
	<remove name="HIDDEN DUMMY"/>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event load="GUARD_FEDERATION"/>
	</choice>
</event>

<event name="GUARD_FEDERATION">
	<text>This sector is protected by a Federation guard. Several support ships linger in the background, offering aid to other Federation ships in the district.</text>
	<modifyPursuit amount="-2"/>
	<choice>
		<text>Request support.</text>
		<event load="GUARD_FED_SUPPORT"/>
	</choice>
	<choice>
		<text>Attack the guard.</text>
		<event>
			<text>The guard's captain is shocked that you've turned on them. "You must be a Rebel spy! We won't take this lightly!"</text>
			<ship hostile="true"/>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice>
		<text>Ignore the guard.</text>
		<event>
			<text>You now have some time to do something on the ship.</text>
			<choice>
				<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
				<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
			<choice>
				<text>Do nothing.</text>
				<event/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>

<event name="GUARD_FED_SUPPORT">
	<text>The guard puts you on a secure line with one of the nearby support ships, who awaits your command.</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Repairs.</text>
		<event>
			<text>Several repair drones are dispatched to repair you.</text>
			<damage amount="-5"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Fuel.</text>
		<event>
			<text>A refueling drone is dispatched to refuel your ship.</text>
			<item_modify>
				<item type="fuel" min="3" max="3"/>
			</item_modify>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Ammo.</text>
		<event>
			<text>A resupply drone is dispatched to resupply your ship.</text>
			<item_modify>
				<item type="missiles" min="2" max="2"/>
			</item_modify>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Droneparts.</text>
		<event>
			<text>A resupply drone is dispatched to resupply your ship.</text>
			<item_modify>
				<item type="drones" min="2" max="2"/>
			</item_modify>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>

<ship name="SHIP_GUARD_FED" auto_blueprint="MU_FED_GUARD">
	<surrender min="999" max="999" load="GUARD_SIGNAL"/>
	<destroyed load="GUARD_FED_DESTROY"/>
	<deadCrew load="GUARD_FED_DEADCREW"/>
</ship>

<event name="GUARD_FED_DESTROY">
	<text>You have defeated the Federation guard. Whatever might have been in their cargo has for certain been destroyed, but you can at least salvage some supplies from the ship.</text>
	<autoReward level="MED">standard</autoReward>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event load="GUARD_FEDERATION_FOLLOWUP"/>
	</choice>
</event>
<event name="GUARD_FED_DEADCREW">
	<text>You have defeated the Federation guard. Without crew on-board to stop you, you can investigate their cargo. You find a weapon to bring back to the ship, and move on to scrap their hull.</text>
	<autoReward level="MED">standard</autoReward>
	<weapon name="GIFTLIST_FEDERATION"/>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event load="GUARD_FEDERATION_FOLLOWUP"/>
	</choice>
</event>

<ship name="SHIP_FED_REINFORCEMENTS" auto_blueprint="LIST_SHIPS_FED_ELITE_FIGHT">
	<destroyed load="DESTROYED_REINFORCEMENTS"/>
	<deadCrew load="DEADCREW_REINFORCEMENTS"/>
</ship>
<event name="GUARD_FEDERATION_FOLLOWUP">
	<noQuestText/>
	<removeHazards/>
	<text>By killing the Federation guard, you have no doubt caused them to dispatch reinforcements to track you down. Watch your step as you explore the sector.</text>
	<quest event="REINFORCEMENTS_FED"/>
	<choice>
		<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
		<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
	</choice>
	<choice>
		<text>Do nothing.</text>
		<event/>
	</choice>
</event>
<event name="REINFORCEMENTS_FED">
	<preventQuest/>
	<beaconType id="map_icon_reinforcements" global="true" req="LOOT_COMPASS">
		<color r="200" g="55" b="82" a="1"/>
		<unvisitedTooltip>An unvisited location.</unvisitedTooltip>
		<visitedTooltip>Explored location. Nothing left of interest.</visitedTooltip>
		<undiscoveredTooltip>An unvisited location.</undiscoveredTooltip>
	</beaconType>
	<text>You catch sight of a rare Federation Elite, but they don't seem pleased to see you. "Turncoats! You should be ashamed!" The ship moves in to attack, and it doesn't take long for you to realize this is one of the ships sent by the guards to hunt you down for attacking.</text>
	<ship load="SHIP_FED_REINFORCEMENTS" hostile="true"/>
	<environment type="PDS" target="player"/>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
	</choice>
</event>


